    {
      "id": "PopularPost116613",
      "post_content": "Would this really be *that* much more playable as an instant?  \n  \nAdditional benefits of this being an instant:  \n- Could use tap abilities of creatures you just played in response to opponent's removal/combat tricks if you hadn't already played this  \n- Could use tap abilities of creatures you just played during opponent's turn  \nThat's pretty much it.  \nI'm not saying these wouldn't be useful, but I don't see it making the difference between playable and not.",
      "posted_by": "Artscrafter",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost116613\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">Would this really be <i>that</i> much more playable as an instant?<br/><br/>Additional benefits of this being an instant:<br/>- Could use tap abilities of creatures you just played in response to opponent's removal/combat tricks if you hadn't already played this<br/>- Could use tap abilities of creatures you just played during opponent's turn<br/>That's pretty much it.<br/>I'm not saying these wouldn't be useful, but I don't see it making the difference between playable and not.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '116613'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy38728\">Artscrafter</span>\r\n                                (11/18/2010 1:52:41 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"