    {
      "id": "PopularPost136111",
      "post_content": "While perhaps not great for standard, there are some environments where this card really shines--the \"casual\" 1.5 environment I play in has so much board wipe ([Planar Cleansing](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Planar Cleansing), [Oblivion Stone](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Oblivion Stone), etc.) That it's practically every other turn that the board disappears, and enchantments aren't safe from it. Therefore being able to have an unexpected attack and get some damage in before the board is wiped again is incredibly useful.",
      "posted_by": "RuthieA",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost136111\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">While perhaps not great for standard, there are some environments where this card really shines--the \"casual\" 1.5 environment I play in has so much board wipe (<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Planar Cleansing\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Planar Cleansing\">Planar Cleansing</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Oblivion Stone\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Oblivion Stone\">Oblivion Stone</a>, etc.) That it's practically every other turn that the board disappears, and enchantments aren't safe from it. Therefore being able to have an unexpected attack and get some damage in before the board is wiped again is incredibly useful.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '136111'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy2340\">RuthieA</span>\r\n                                (2/9/2011 11:29:49 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popula