      "id": "PopularPost156208",
      "post_content": "Here's my favorite combo:\n  \n   \n[Wooded Foothills](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wooded Foothills) -> [Fastbond](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fastbond) -> 2 non-tapping lands -> [Crucible of Worlds](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Crucible of Worlds) -> [Rampaging Baloths](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rampaging Baloths) -> [Burst of Speed](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Burst of Speed)   \nThen attack for game.\n  \n   ",
      "posted_by": "Feralsymphony",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost156208\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_post\">Here's my favorite combo:\r<br/> <br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Wooded Foothills\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wooded Foothills\">Wooded Foothills</a> -&gt; <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Fastbond\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fastbond\">Fastbond</a> -&gt; 2 non-tapping lands -&gt; <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Crucible of Worlds\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Crucible of Worlds\">Crucible of Worlds</a> -&gt; <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Rampaging Baloths\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rampaging Baloths\">Rampaging Baloths</a> -&gt; <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Burst of Speed\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Burst of Speed\">Burst of Speed</a> <br/>Then attack for game.\r<br/> <br/></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '156208'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy54664\">Feralsymphony</span>\r\n                                (4/29/2011 3:44:50 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"flo