      "id": "PopularPost173486",
      "post_content": "Neither [Accelerate](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Accelerate) nor this saw any play. But had this stayed at R *and* cantripped, we might see those professional players start getting creative about possible uses.\n  \n   \nTo date, there was only one one-use haste spell (as opposed to a permanent one like [Yavimaya Fires](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Yavimaya Fires)) that saw any significant play IIRC: [Reckless Charge](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Reckless Charge). That was one awesome card.",
      "posted_by": "Gabriel422",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost173486\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">Neither <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Accelerate\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Accelerate\">Accelerate</a> nor this saw any play. But had this stayed at R <i>and</i> cantripped, we might see those professional players start getting creative about possible uses.\r<br/> <br/>To date, there was only one one-use haste spell (as opposed to a permanent one like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Yavimaya Fires\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Yavimaya Fires\">Yavimaya Fires</a>) that saw any significant play IIRC: <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Reckless Charge\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Reckless Charge\">Reckless Charge</a>. That was one awesome card.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '173486'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy42139\">Gabriel422</span>\r\n                                (6/29/2011 12:37:09 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00