    {
      "id": "PopularPost238097",
      "post_content": "@toollins - I'm not sure... while Burst of Speed does give all of your creatures Haste, it's not an instant.  \n[Surge of Zeal](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Surge of Zeal) (which *is* an instant) works well in decks where most of your creatures share at least *one* color, or if like the deck I'm trying to rebuild, you run a quartet of multicolored creatures whose participation helps the team (such as [Lightning Angel](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Angel) or [Skyknight Legionnaire](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Skyknight Legionnaire)).  \n  \nBecause I'm looking it up for a {R/W} deck with lots of Goblins, I'm thinking of running one of each.",
      "posted_by": "Cybertronian",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost238097\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_post\">@toollins - I'm not sure... while Burst of Speed does give all of your creatures Haste, it's not an instant.<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Surge of Zeal\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Surge of Zeal\">Surge of Zeal</a> (which <i>is</i> an instant) works well in decks where most of your creatures share at least <i>one</i> color, or if like the deck I'm trying to rebuild, you run a quartet of multicolored creatures whose participation helps the team (such as <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Lightning Angel\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Angel\">Lightning Angel</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Skyknight Legionnaire\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Skyknight Legionnaire\">Skyknight Legionnaire</a>).<br/><br/>Because I'm looking it up for a {R/W} deck with lots of Goblins, I'm thinking of running one of each.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '238097'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy3000\">Cybertronian</span>\r\n                                (4/16/2012 9:22:34 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n            