    {
      "id": "PopularPost17232",
      "post_content": "Interesting card. It's perfectly priced, and it has a reasonable effect. Unfortunately, like many of the cards in this set, there's one cost that makes it unplayable-- the cost of a card. Frankly, as reasonable as this card is, 1 card for this effect just isn't worthwhile. A card that said \"Prevent 1 damage\" and cost 0 wouldn't be playable either-- no one would argue that the price was wrong, just that in a 60 card deck it's not worth a slot. Same thing here.",
      "posted_by": "TroglodyteJB",
