      "post_content": "@Demonic\\_Math\\_Tutor  \nNice one, though technically that could be achieved by any 1 CMC red card that gives haste to one creature, which there are a lot of. I thought of this:  \n  \nTurn 1  \nMountain, [Ornithopter](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ornithopter), [Ornithopter](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ornithopter)  \n[Infernal Plunge](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Infernal Plunge), sac an [Ornithopter](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ornithopter), repeat  \n5 {R} in mana pool. Play [Empty the Warrens](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Empty the Warrens) and this  \nSwing for 8  \n  \n[Goblin War Strike](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Goblin War Strike) would work in place of this, though.",
      "posted_by": "tankthebest",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost234167\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_post\">@Demonic_Math_Tutor<br/>Nice one, though technically that could be achieved by any 1 CMC red card that gives haste to one creature, which there are a lot of. I thought of this:<br/><br/>Turn 1<br/>Mountain, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Ornithopter\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ornithopter\">Ornithopter</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Ornithopter\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ornithopter\">Ornithopter</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Infernal Plunge\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Infernal Plunge\">Infernal Plunge</a>, sac an <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Ornithopter\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ornithopter\">Ornithopter</a>, repeat<br/>5 {R} in mana pool. Play <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Empty the Warrens\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Empty the Warrens\">Empty the Warrens</a> and this<br/>Swing for 8<br/><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Goblin War Strike\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Goblin War Strike\">Goblin War Strike</a> would work in place of this, though.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '234167'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                  